User (Frontend)
    │
    ▼
HTML/CSS/JS UI
    │  Sends requests (Fetch API)
    ▼
Backend Server (Node.js + Express)
    │
    │  Handles API routes:
    │    GET /products       → fetch all products
    │    GET /suppliers      → fetch all suppliers
    │    POST /purchaseorders → create new purchase order
    │    POST /products/:id/receive → update stock
    ▼
SQL Server Database
    │
    │  Tables:
    │    Suppliers
    │    Products
    │    PurchaseOrders
    │    OrderDetails
    │
    │  Stored Procedures:
    │    sp_CreatePurchaseOrder
    │    sp_UpdateStock
    │
    │  Trigger:
    │    trg_AutoReorder → auto creates order if stock < reorder level
    ▼
Database updates / responses
    │
    ▼
Frontend UI updates in real-time
